# E2E Cockpit — @@APP_NAME@@ (Project Topology Overlay)

> Load the **global** `e2e-cockpit` skill first for the generic overseer protocol,
> dispatch patterns, question protocol, and triage workflow.
> This file adds the `@@APP_NAME@@`-specific topology on top.
> Use `cockpit-overseer loop` for compact status checks instead of re-capturing
> full panes in a loop.

> **If you are in `worker-test`** — load the `e2e-operator` skill instead.

