## Running tests

```bash
# From the e2e/ directory
./run-audit.sh --scope "@smoke"   # smoke gate (always first)
./run-audit.sh                    # full suite
./run-playwright.sh --grep @smoke # ad-hoc
```

For overseer status, prefer:

```bash
cockpit-overseer loop --session "<session>" --window worker-test --window worker-dev --window worker-fix
```

Prerequisites:
1. Backend reachable → `curl -sk http://localhost:@@BACKEND_PORT@@@@HEALTH_PATH@@` returns 200
2. `e2e/.env.local` with `FRONTEND_URL`, `BACKEND_URL`, `SKIP_DB_RESET=true`
